    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Scenario 2",
    "long_instructions": "*Review the scenario below and use the AI Chat to learn more in-depth about this threat:*\r\n\r\n## Scenario 2\r\n\r\nA large hospital network’s IT department notices unusual activity late at night. \r\n\r\nWhen doctors arrive in the morning, they can’t access patient records, lab results, or appointment systems. \r\n\r\nAll hospital monitors display the same note: \r\n“Your files have been encrypted. Pay $5 million in Bitcoin within 72 hours or all data will be lost.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://images.code.org/b16c76b9403264fc2940faf2fab6b73b-image-1752764768757.05.25 AM.png\" alt=\"computer monitor locked with a price tag\" width=\"300\"/>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Chat with an Expert: Digital Forensics Analyst\r\n\r\nA **digital forensics analyst** investigates cyber incidents by collecting and analyzing digital evidence to uncover how an attack happened and who was responsible.\r\n",
    "aichat_settings": {
      "initialCustomizations": {
        "selectedModelId": "gpt-4o-mini",
        "temperature": 0.3,
        "systemPrompt": "",
        "retrievalContexts": [

